```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client (Phone)
    participant Node as Extender Node

    Note over Node: Power On / First Boot
    Node->>Node: Read NVS; 'is_adopted' is false or missing
    Node->>Node: Enter 'Unadopted' State

    loop Physical 'Tap-to-Wake'
        Node->>Node: Wake from Deep Sleep via EXT0
        Node->>Node: Start BLE Advertising ('Azul-Extender')
    end

    Client->>Node: Scans and initiates first connection
    Node-->>Client: Connection established

    alt 'Unadopted' State
        Client->>Client: Generate unique GUID
        Client->>Node: Write GUID to 'Authentication' Characteristic
        Node->>Node: Store GUID in NVS<br>Set 'is_adopted' flag to true
        Node-->>Client: Acknowledge successful adoption
        Node->>Node: Transition to 'Adopted' State
    end

    Note over Node,Client: -- Subsequent Connections --

    loop Physical 'Tap-to-Wake'
        Node->>Node: Wake and start BLE Advertising
    end

    Client->>Node: Connects with stored GUID
    Node->>Node: Validate incoming GUID against NVS
    
    alt GUID Matches
        Node-->>Client: Authentication Success<br>Allow operations
    else GUID Mismatches
        Node-->>Client: Authentication Failure<br>Ignore 'Write' commands
    end
```
